=========
djcorecap
=========

Core app for Django projects that provides essential functions, tags, and enhanced Bootstrap-friendly templates.

* Free software: MIT license


Features
--------

* Custom base template that plays nicely with Bootstrap (and themes like startbootstrap)
* Custom allauth templates that play nicely with Bootstrap (and themes like startbootstrap)
* Convenience functions to support Bokeh plots
* Template tag for auto-setting links to active
